| Offering PII anonymization as a SaaS to customers | **Yes — commercial license required** |
| Embedding Nonym in a commercial product | **Yes — commercial license required** |
| Building a competing managed PII service | **Yes — commercial license required** |
| Redistribution as part of a commercial offering | **Yes — commercial license required** |
